{"data":[{"date":"08:53 23/07","title":"HLV Miura n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u00ec thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/24/hlv-miura-noi-gi-khi-chung-kien-hoc-tro-da-tho-bao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n v\u00ec l\u1ed7i v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o, HLV Toshiya Miura \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa CLB TP.HCM v\u00e0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 22/7, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 chung cu\u1ed9c nh\u1edd c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh Matias Gonzalez. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Miura \u0111\u00e3 b\u1edbt ph\u1ea7n lung linh khi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf v\u00ec l\u1ed7i v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ngh\u1ec7 An b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Toshiya Miura n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u00ec thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Toshiya Miura n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u00ec thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/hlv-miura-noi-gi-khi-chung-kien-hoc-tro-da-tho-bao.jpg\" /></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Toshiya Miura l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 sau t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 pha v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c, HLV Miura \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan s\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3 n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ebb. Sau pha b\u00f3ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, ch\u01b0a chia s\u1ebb \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0110\u1ee9c.\u00a0<o:p></o:p>Trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, t\u00f4i mong Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c tinh th\u1ea7n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn h\u01a1n v\u1edbi anh ta\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HLV Miura cho th\u1ea5y nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng x\u1ea5u x\u00ed,\u00a0\u0111\u00e1ng l\u00ean \u00e1n c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7.\u00a0<o:p></o:p>V\u1edbi t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t n\u00e0y, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i treo gi\u00f2 v\u00e0i tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i V-League. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t l\u1edbn cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t khi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i th\u00eam v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, HLV Miura cho hay: \u00a0\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 CLB ph\u1ea3i tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nh\u00f3m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf. Hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1eeba qua th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, n\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. V\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o 6 tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cK\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi, h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian ho\u00e0 nh\u1eadp. Nh\u01b0 Quang Huy ho\u1eb7c Marclei Santos ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n. Kesley th\u00ec t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00ec anh ta bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t. D\u00f9 sao \u0111i n\u1eefa, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 qu\u00e3ng ngh\u0129 ASIAD \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt\u201d, \u00f4ng Miura ch\u1ed1t l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB TP.HCM l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 11 v\u1edbi 21 \u0111i\u1ec3m, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 t\u1edbi 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/tphcm-vs-quang-ninh-vong-20-vleague-2018-372-191786.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/tphcm-vs-quang-ninh-vong-20-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/tphcm-vs-quang-ninh-vong-20-vleague-2018-372-191786.html\">TPHCM 2-1 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh (KT): V\u01b0\u1ee3t kh\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Miura l\u1ea1i tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nh\u00f3m nguy hi\u1ec3m</span><br />\r\nC\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Matias Jadue gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Toshiya Miura th\u1eafng 2-1 khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 20 gi\u1ea3i Nuti Caf\u00e9 V-League 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4511","checkdouble":"191820"},{"date":"07:51 23/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 23/7: Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/18/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-237-tiet-lo-3-muc-tieu-cung-co-hang-thu-cua-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 23/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>B\u1ecb CLB M\u1ef9 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a, M.U c\u00f2n m\u1ea5t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. </strong>Man United ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc SJ Earthquakes. H\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef khi Antonio Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eafp ch\u00e2n v\u00e0 s\u1edbm r\u1eddi s\u00e2n gi\u1eefa ch\u1eebng.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nTi\u1ebft l\u1ed9 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a M.U. </strong>Manchester United \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Harry Maguire, Toby Alderweireld ho\u1eb7c Leonardo Bonucci. Nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 \u00f4ng quy\u1ebft mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf t\u1eeb gi\u1edd t\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 237 Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 237 Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/18/Thuong-vu-MU-mua-Leonardo-Bonucci-co-dien-bien-moi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Bonucci l\u00e0 1 trong 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nSao Man City ghen t\u1ecb v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. </strong>Aymeric Laporte ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ghen t\u1ecb v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Les Bleus khi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 mang v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u cho Liverpool.</strong> Liverpool \u0111ang nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 Domagoj Vida c\u1ee7a Besiktas. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Steve Nicol tin r\u1eb1ng Liverpool c\u1ea7n mua Diego Godin c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi Barca. </strong>Yerry Mina s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Barca. Everton \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng anh gia nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu l\u00e0 c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barcelona cho h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Yerry Mina cua Barca\" title=\"Yerry Mina cua Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/sao-sang-world-cup-thua-nhan-co-the-bi-da-khoi-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Yerry Mina s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Matip quy\u1ebft c\u1ea1nh tranh su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Liverpool. </strong>Cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Liverpool m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trung v\u1ec7 Joel Matip kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Lovren, Van Dijk r\u1ed3i Klavan, Gomez cho m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong danh s\u00e1ch du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Juventus.</strong> Nh\u1eefng ai tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa Real Madrid vs Juventus s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. L\u00fd do n\u1eb1m \u1edf ch\u1ed7 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng Cristiano Ronaldo c\u1ee7a Juve s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ph\u00e9p sau khi d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4510","checkdouble":"191814"},{"date":"08:19 23/07","title":"T\u1ea1o k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u1edf World Cup, HLV Croatia t\u1ef1 l\u00e0m gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/16/tao-ky-tich-o-world-cup-hlv-croatia-tu-lam-gia-ban-than.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Zlatko Dalic kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 HLV xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao h\u01a1n 5 tri\u1ec7u USD/n\u0103m.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Dalic l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a Croatia</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hau-chung-ket-world-cup-2018-khi-nguoi-thang-va-ke-thua-deu-do-ra-duong-465-191335.html\" target=\"_blank\">Croatia l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u1edf World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n</span> v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. Ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 vi\u1ebft n\u00ean c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ed5 t\u00edch cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Balkan l\u00e0 Luka Modric, l\u00e0 Ivan Raktitic v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u00ednh HLV Zlatko Dalic.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 52 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ch\u1eefa ch\u00e1y c\u1ee7a L\u0110B\u0110 Croatia c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ed9t n\u0103m sau khi sa th\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m Ante Cacic v\u00ec th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ebft b\u00e1t \u1edf chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Dalic chia tay Croatia v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 l\u00e0m gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Dalic chia tay Croatia v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 l\u00e0m gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/tao-ky-tich-o-world-cup-hlv-croatia-tu-lam-gia-ban-than.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Dalic chia tay Croatia \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00ednh m\u1ed9t Dalic v\u00f4 danh t\u1eeb th\u1eddi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ebfn HLV n\u00e0y (7 n\u0103m l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c Trung \u0110\u00f4ng) \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Croatia v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1eeda t\u1eed \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i m\u1ed9t m\u1ea1ch t\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tranh c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Dalic \u00fap m\u1edf chuy\u1ec7n ra \u0111i, t\u1ef1 l\u00e0m gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa \u00fd h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u sau m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng h\u00e8 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u00f9ng Croatia, Dalic gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt nh\u1ea5t L\u0110B\u0110 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Ai C\u1eadp c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 CLB Premier League nghi\u00eam t\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft. Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i l\u00e0m gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;C\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn hay kh\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111ang l\u00e0 HLV xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u1eady th\u00ec con s\u1ed1 5 tri\u1ec7u USD/n\u0103m d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 v\u1ebb t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u00edt \u1ecfi so v\u1edbi ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 l\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ed5ng m\u00e0 HLV xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c quan tr\u1ecdng th\u1eadt nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i c\u00f2n hai n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Croatia v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh n\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng Ba r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o.&rdquo; &ndash; Dalic b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bai-hoc-tu-nguoi-croatia-dat-nuoc-nho-giac-mo-lon-421-191456.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/bai-hoc-tu-nguoi-croatia-dat-nuoc-nho-giac-mo-lon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bai-hoc-tu-nguoi-croatia-dat-nuoc-nho-giac-mo-lon-421-191456.html\">B\u00e0i h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia: \u0110\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1ecf, gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 l\u1edbn</span><br>\r\n&ldquo;Mala zemlja, veliki snovi&rdquo; &ndash; D\u00f2ng ch\u1eef ti\u1ebfng Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean xe bus ch\u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia rong ru\u1ed5i c\u1ea3 th\u00e1ng h\u00e8 qua tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. D\u1ecbch ra ti\u1ebfng Vi\u1ec7t:...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4509","checkdouble":"191815"},{"date":"07:20 23/07","title":"B\u1ecb CLB M\u1ef9 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a, M.U c\u00f2n m\u1ea5t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/bi-clb-my-cam-hoa-mu-con-mat-tru-cot-do-chan-thuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man United ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc SJ Earthquakes. H\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef khi Antonio Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eafp ch\u00e2n v\u00e0 s\u1edbm r\u1eddi s\u00e2n gi\u1eefa ch\u1eebng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Valencia ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 7 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi SJ Earthquakes t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Levi trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu, Antonio Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Man United bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Matteo Darmian.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Valencia v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9. HLV Jose Mourinho lo ng\u1ea1i r\u1eb1ng anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c khi M.U ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Leicester City t\u1edbi s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 10 th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU b\u1ecb CLB M\u1ef9 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a, Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU b\u1ecb CLB M\u1ef9 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a, Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/Valencia-roi-san-do-chan-thuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>M.U g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t Valencia do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, HLV Mourinho c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea7y lo l\u1eafng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a M.U. Sau khi v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 v\u1edbi Club America, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc SJ Earthquakes.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong su\u1ed1t 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, d\u00f9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c hay d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, M.U \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu. Ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 Alexis Sanchez m\u1edbi t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 t\u1eadp trung song kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xoay chuy\u1ec3n th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Qua nhieu bai toan hoc bua cho HLV Jose Mourinho truoc mua giai moi\" title=\"Qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i to\u00e1n h\u00f3c b\u00faa cho HLV Jose Mourinho tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/MU-0-0-San-Jose-Earthquakes-Them-mot-tran-giao-huu-that-vong-cua-bay-Quy-do-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Mourinho nhi\u1ec1u lo l\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a m\u1edbi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi Sanchez r\u1eddi s\u00e2n ph\u00fat 65, th\u1ebf c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a M.U c\u0169ng y\u1ebfu h\u1eb3n \u0111i. Anthony Martial \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ee7 90 ph\u00fat song kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tung ra n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Tahith Chong, Mason Greenwood r\u1ed3i Angel Gomes&hellip; c\u0169ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSu\u1ed1t 90 ph\u00fat, M.U ch\u1ec9 tung ra c\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang 1 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch. Vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd b\u1ecb SJ Earthquakes c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u00f9 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u01b0ng l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Man United tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-00-san-jose-earthquakes-giao-huu-he-2018-326-191811.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: MU 0-0 San Jose Earthquakes (Giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dam-phan-chieu-mo-sao-khung-mu-172-191806.html\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao kh\u1ee7ng MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jurgen-klopp-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-chuyen-nhuong-cua-liverpool-172-191802.html\">B\u1ecb ch\u00ea mua Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft, Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u1ed5 t\u1ed9i cho... Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-san-jose-earthquakes-giao-huu-he-2018-372-191798.html\">MU 0-0 San Jose Earthquakes: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4508","checkdouble":"191813"},{"date":"08:16 23/07","title":"Mourinho b\u00e0o ch\u1eefa th\u1ebf n\u00e0o sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a th\u1ee9 2 t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/mourinho-bao-chua-the-nao-sau-tran-hoa-thu-2-tai-my.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn M.U 0-0 SJ Earthquakes. \u00d4ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a khi \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nM.U b\u1ecb SJ Earthquakes c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi b\u1ecb Club America c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1, Man United l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc San Jose Earthquakes. S\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 th\u01b0a th\u1edbt t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Levi d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u t\u1ebb nh\u1ea1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 M.U d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n song kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 tung ra c\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang 1 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, \u00edt h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi SJ Earthquakes.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn MU 0-0 SJ Earthquakes h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn MU 0-0 SJ Earthquakes h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/Jose-Mourinho-phat-bieu-sau-tran-MU-0-0-SJ-Earthquakes-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sanchez kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap M.U th\u1eafng SJ Earthquakes</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c M.U h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cho nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00ednh c\u1ea3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ebb nh\u1ea1t v\u1edbi Club America, vi\u1ec7c th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jose Mourinho li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u00f3 2 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a khi \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nMourinho kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn M.U 0-0 SJ Earthquakes. \u00d4ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 mong \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eadp n\u1eefa&rdquo;, Mourinho n\u00f3i v\u1edbi k\u00eanh MUTV. &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c nhau. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i 1, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 U23, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u1ec1 ho\u1eb7c m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i khi cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00f2n d\u01b0\u1edbi 18 tu\u1ed5i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho tai My\" title=\"Mourinho tai My\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/mourinho-bao-chua-the-nao-sau-tran-hoa-thu-2-tai-my.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn M.U 0-0 SJ Earthquakes</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAlexis Sanchez v\u00e0 Andreas Pereira l\u00e0 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc SJ Earthquakes. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khen t\u1eeb th\u1ea7y Mourinho. &ldquo;Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t&rdquo;, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam. &ldquo;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i sau m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp ri\u00eang. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Sanchez c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng khen.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Pereira c\u0169ng \u1ed5n, t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh, mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Man United tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-00-san-jose-earthquakes-giao-huu-he-2018-326-191811.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: MU 0-0 San Jose Earthquakes (Giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dam-phan-chieu-mo-sao-khung-mu-172-191806.html\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao kh\u1ee7ng MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-san-jose-earthquakes-giao-huu-he-2018-372-191798.html\">MU 0-0 San Jose Earthquakes: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-mu-lo-so-bi-cac-tai-nang-tre-dan-em-cuop-cho-172-191775.html\">Sao MU lo s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb c\u00e1c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb \u0111\u00e0n em c\u01b0\u1edbp ch\u1ed7</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4507","checkdouble":"191817"},{"date":"08:49 23/07","title":"MU l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, Mourinho c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Martial","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/23/mu-lai-gay-that-vong-mourinho-canh-bao-martial.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean \u1edf tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i v\u00e0 gia nh\u1eadp m\u1ed9t \u00f4ng l\u1edbn Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u kh\u00e1c m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Khi Romelu Lukaku v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9, Anthony Martial \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p HLV Jose Mourinho ch\u1ec9 g\u00f3i g\u1ecdn trong s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Martial sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a MU 0-0 San Jose h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mourinho c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Martial sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a MU 0-0 San Jose h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/mu-lai-gay-that-vong-mourinho-canh-bao-martial.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Martial sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a MU 0-0 San Jose</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Man Utd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ebf t\u1eafc, ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-san-jose-earthquakes-giao-huu-he-2018-372-191798.html\" target=\"_blank\">CLB M\u1ef9 San Jose Earthquakes c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 0-0</span>. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u1edf IC Cup 2018, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu th\u01b0\u1eddng ni\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Martial nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1edbi \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1ng c\u1ed5 anh ra kh\u1ecfi Old Trafford. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i nh\u1eb1m c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, v\u1eady n\u00ean Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1eb7c Bi\u1ec7t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m giam c\u1ea7m c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ee9 mu\u1ed1n g\u00ec l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ea5y. Nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e2y n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea3 5 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Los Angeles, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i di chuy\u1ec3n hay thay \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i c\u1ee9 th\u1ebf tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Manchester chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng, gi\u1edd t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf San Jose v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Premier League v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i th\u1ee9 s\u00e1u.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Martial \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103m tia nghi\u00eam t\u00fac b\u1edfi Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, Man Utd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00f4ng \u201cn\u1ed1i gi\u00e1o cho gi\u1eb7c\u201d trong l\u00f2ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u00e0 b\u00e1n anh cho Bayern Munich.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/23/MU-1-0-San-Jose.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4506","checkdouble":"191818"},{"date":"21:19 22/07","title":"Cristiano Ronaldo s\u1ebd ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam kho\u1ea3ng bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n cho Juventus?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/cristiano-ronaldo-kiem-them-bao-nhieu-tien-cho-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ecf ra 100 tri\u1ec7u euro, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7t ra c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi li\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 b\u00e0i to\u00e0n kinh t\u1ebf, Cristiano Ronaldo ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n cho Juventus \u1edf nh\u1eefng n\u0103m ti\u1ebfp theo?</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cristiano Ronaldo ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n cho Juventus?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i, Juventus t\u1eebng khi\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng nh\u00e2n \u1edf nh\u00e0 m\u00e1y xe h\u01a1i FIAT \u0111\u00ecnh c\u00f4ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean sau \u0111\u00f3, cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00ecnh c\u00f4ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng tho\u00e1i tr\u00e0o khi Ronaldo cho th\u1ea5y anh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 t\u1ea1o ra hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf m\u00e0 c\u00f2n tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam b\u1ed9n ti\u1ec1n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n cho Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n cho Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/cristiano-ronaldo-kiem-them-bao-nhieu-tien-cho-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi Cristiano Ronaldo ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n cho Juventus, t\u1edd Il Sole 24 Ore th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea r\u1eb1ng m\u1ed7i n\u0103m, &quot;b\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0&quot; s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam 75 \u0111\u1ebfn 100 tri\u1ec7u euro. Trong \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n v\u00e9 v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh, Juventus s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam 34 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u1ed7i n\u0103m nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Ronaldo c\u00f2n gi\u00fap t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u cho Juventus. Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Juventus tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng l\u00ean kho\u1ea3ng 15% so v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1edd v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo d\u00f5i \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o, l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn con s\u1ed1 h\u01a1n 200 tri\u1ec7u tr\u00ean Twitter v\u00e0 Instagram g\u1ed9p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCon g\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebb tr\u1ee9ng v\u00e0ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay trong 24 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Turin, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Juventus b\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 520.000 \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u, thu v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3ng m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n ba s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. B\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Juventus c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 5 trong top nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean Instagram.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ramon Calderon, c\u1ef1u Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Real Madrid ph\u1ea3i th\u1ed1t l\u00ean r\u1eb1ng b\u00e1n Ronaldo l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m l\u1ecbch s\u1eed khi t\u1eb7ng &quot;con g\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebb tr\u1ee9ng v\u00e0ng&quot; cho Juvetus. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Real Madrid v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/deschamps-cac-hoc-tro-cua-toi-xung-dang-gianh-bong-vang-hon-ronaldo-messi-184-191751.html\">Deschamps: C\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng h\u01a1n Ronaldo, Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-no-luc-chieu-mo-sat-thu-serie-a-180-191701.html\">Real mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 &ldquo;s\u00e1t th\u1ee7&rdquo; Serie A \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/neymar-tin-ronaldo-se-toa-sang-tren-dat-y-176-191698.html\">Neymar tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t \u00dd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/ronaldo-cap-ben-turin-juve-co-con-la-juve-389-191603.html\">Ronaldo c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Turin:  Juve c\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0&hellip; Juve?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/ngoi-sao-ronaldo-bi-in-mat-len-giay-ve-sinh-188-191598.html\">Ng\u00f4i sao Ronaldo b\u1ecb in m\u1eb7t l\u00ean ... gi\u1ea5y v\u1ec7 sinh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chu-tich-real-madrid-hua-se-no-bom-tan-khoa-lap-ronaldo-180-191561.html\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Real Madrid h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4505","checkdouble":"191796"},{"date":"22:15 22/07","title":"Cristiano Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/22/juventus-e.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eefng ai tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa Real Madrid vs Juventus s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 d\u1ef1 ICC 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang ch\u1ee7 Juventus c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt, danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham gia chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 t\u1ea1i Hoa K\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 th\u00eam sau World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/juventus-e.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Juventus t\u1ea1i Hoa K\u1ef3.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Ronaldo, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ed3m Paulo Dybala, Gonzalo Higuain, Juan Cuadrado, Rodrigo Bentancur v\u00e0 Douglas Costa c\u0169ng s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t. Nh\u00f3m n\u00e0y s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Juventus v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng khi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Mario Mandzukic, Marko Pjaca (Croatia) v\u00e0 Blaise Matuidi (Ph\u00e1p) s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. C\u1ea3 ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 th\u00eam v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ecbch tr\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Juventus t\u1ea1i ICC 2018<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo l\u1ecbch tr\u00ecnh, Juventus s\u1ebd c\u00f3 b\u1ed1n tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9. Trong \u0111\u00f3, ba tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 ICC 2018 g\u1ed3m g\u1eb7p Bayern Munich (6h05 ng\u00e0y 26/7), Benfica (6h05 ng\u00e0y 29/7) v\u00e0 Real Madrid (5h05 ng\u00e0y 5/8).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xen l\u1eabn v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, Juventus s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn MLS (gi\u1ea3i nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9) di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 6h30 ng\u00e0y 2/8.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd tham gia chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Juventus g\u1ed3m Szczesny, De Sciglio, Chiellini, Benatia, Pjanic, Khedira, Marchisio, Alex Sandro, Caldara, Barzagli, Perin, Joao Cancelo, Pinsoglio, Emre Can, Rugani, Betuatto, Del Favero, Bernardeschi, Fernandes, Macek, Kastanos, Clemenza, Pereira, Beltrame, Favilli, Di Pardo, Fagioli.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-kiem-them-bao-nhieu-tien-cho-juventus-176-191796.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo s\u1ebd ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam kho\u1ea3ng bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n cho Juventus?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/deschamps-cac-hoc-tro-cua-toi-xung-dang-gianh-bong-vang-hon-ronaldo-messi-184-191751.html\">Deschamps: C\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng h\u01a1n Ronaldo, Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-no-luc-chieu-mo-sat-thu-serie-a-180-191701.html\">Real mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u201cs\u00e1t th\u1ee7\u201d Serie A \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/neymar-tin-ronaldo-se-toa-sang-tren-dat-y-176-191698.html\">Neymar tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t \u00dd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/ronaldo-cap-ben-turin-juve-co-con-la-juve-389-191603.html\">Ronaldo c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Turin:  Juve c\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0\u2026 Juve?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/ngoi-sao-ronaldo-bi-in-mat-len-giay-ve-sinh-188-191598.html\">Ng\u00f4i sao Ronaldo b\u1ecb in m\u1eb7t l\u00ean ... gi\u1ea5y v\u1ec7 sinh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4504","checkdouble":"191800"},{"date":"21:02 22/07","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb quay l\u01b0ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/hlv-park-hang-seo-so-bi-quay-lung-ngay-truoc-them-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb quay l\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb quay l\u01b0ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00fap U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0m n\u00ean chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 t\u00f4n vinh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng. S\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng d\u00e0nh cho th\u1ea7y Park c\u00f2n l\u1edbn h\u01a1n n\u1eefa khi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo so bi quay lung neu DT Olympic Viet Nam choi khong tot o ASIAD 2018.\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb quay l\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf ASIAD 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/hlv-park-hang-seo-so-bi-quay-lung-ngay-truoc-them-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb quay l\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf ASIAD 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, th\u1ea7y Park c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u0103n tr\u1edf nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. Nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Jeong Da-woo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb quay l\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u1ea7y Park cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng v\u00ec s\u1ef1 y\u00eau m\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng lu\u00f4n mong manh nh\u01b0 m\u00e2y kh\u00f3i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tan bi\u1ebfn b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 l\u00fac n\u00e0o. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i t\u1eebng tr\u1ea3i qua \u1edf H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2002&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m c\u0169, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia cho bi\u1ebft c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i khi thi\u1ebfu hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Palestine v\u00e0 UAE khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y Park th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea3o l\u1ed9n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Viet Nam nam chung bang voi Nhat Ban tai ASIAD 2018.\" title=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/ldbd-chau-a-afc-noi-gi-ve-kha-nang-boc-tham-lai-asiad.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>B\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 theo l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ban \u0111\u1ea7u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLi\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 (AFC) m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng can thi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. Theo nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edd b\u00e1o trong khu v\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0a tin, Indonesia s\u1ebd t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c b\u1ed1c th\u0103m v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 Hai (23/7) nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 s\u1ebd b\u1ed1c th\u0103m c\u1ea3, hai ch\u1ec9 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n s\u00f3t l\u00e0 UAE v\u00e0 Palestine.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ldbd-chau-a-afc-noi-gi-ve-kha-nang-boc-tham-lai-asiad-168-191785.html\">L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 AFC n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ASIAD?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/boc-tham-lai-asiad-2018-olympic-viet-nam-roi-vao-bang-nao-168-191684.html\">B\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng n\u00e0o?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hang-cong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-ai-se-phai-o-nha-168-191682.html\">H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: Ai s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u1edf nh\u00e0?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-chi-ra-diem-yeu-cua-cau-thu-viet-nam-292-191650.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/do-hung-dung-mot-net-rat-rieng-cua-nguoi-ha-noi-168-191541.html\">\u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng: M\u1ed9t n\u00e9t r\u1ea5t ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-dat-muc-tieu-cho-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-191537.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4503","checkdouble":"191795"},{"date":"21:53 22/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng ai trong \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/26/nhung-ai-trong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-phai-len-tap-trung-muon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tr\u00f9ng l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 13 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng ai ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean mu\u1ed9n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo l\u1ecbch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 23/7 sau v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c hai tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 27/7, 13 trong s\u1ed1 30 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp s\u1ebd l\u00ean mu\u1ed9n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"u23 viet nam\" title=\"u23 vi\u1ec7t nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/7/hlv-le-thuy-hai-nhan-xet-ve-danh-sach-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 13 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n v\u00ec b\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1 b\u00e1n k\u1ebft C\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c gia 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 Thanh H\u00f3a vs SLNA. C\u1ea3 b\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch t\u1eadp trung l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Trong \u0111\u00f3, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p t\u1edbi 8 c\u00e1i t\u00ean, SLNA v\u00e0 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, c\u00f2n Thanh H\u00f3a c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e1m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n g\u1ed3m V\u0103n H\u1eadu, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, Th\u00e0nh Chung, Duy M\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, Quang H\u1ea3i, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Huy. SLNA c\u00f3 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, c\u00f2n B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u00e0 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan kh\u00f4ng g\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 tu\u1ed5i U23<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi th\u00eam 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean l\u1ee9a tu\u1ed5i U23 nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o qu\u00e1 23 tu\u1ed5i. HLV Worrawoot Srimaka \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean danh s\u00e1ch 30 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o tr\u00ean tu\u1ed5i 23.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bang dau cua DT Olympic Viet Nam tai ASIAD 2018.\" title=\"B\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/bang-asiad.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>B\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ban \u0111\u1ea7u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp b\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean tu\u1ed5i 23 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m (H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng), \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i) v\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n Anh \u0110\u1ee9c (B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng).&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ban \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ebd n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Uzbekistan, Bangladesh v\u00e0 Qatar. C\u00f2n \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D c\u00f9ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n khi ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n b\u1ea3ng cho hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ecb s\u00f3t l\u00e0 Palestine v\u00e0 UAE.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-so-bi-quay-lung-ngay-truoc-them-asiad-2018-292-191795.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb quay l\u01b0ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ldbd-chau-a-afc-noi-gi-ve-kha-nang-boc-tham-lai-asiad-168-191785.html\">L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 AFC n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ASIAD?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/boc-tham-lai-asiad-2018-olympic-viet-nam-roi-vao-bang-nao-168-191684.html\">B\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng n\u00e0o?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hang-cong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-ai-se-phai-o-nha-168-191682.html\">H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: Ai s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u1edf nh\u00e0?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-chi-ra-diem-yeu-cua-cau-thu-viet-nam-292-191650.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/do-hung-dung-mot-net-rat-rieng-cua-nguoi-ha-noi-168-191541.html\">\u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng: M\u1ed9t n\u00e9t r\u1ea5t ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4502","checkdouble":"191799"},{"date":"23:29 22/07","title":"HLV Tuchel gi\u1ee5c Rabiot quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/10/8/hlv-tuchel-giuc-rabiot-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Thomas Tuchel hy v\u1ecdng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng Adrien Rabiot s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai r\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barcelona.</h2><h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Rabiot b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u euro. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 La Liga \u0111ang mong mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p cho h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 Paulinho ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Rabiot \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a PSG trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Bayern, HLV Tuchel v\u1eabn th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Tuchel gi\u1ee5c Rabiot quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Tuchel gi\u1ee5c Rabiot quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/8/hlv-tuchel-giuc-rabiot-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Tuchel gi\u1ee5c Rabiot s\u1edbm quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cD\u0129 nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5y ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. V\u00e0 Rabiot c\u0169ng c\u00f2n ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Rabiot th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 ra \u0111i v\u00e0 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m m\u1edbi\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nRabiot \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra m\u1eaft PSG b\u1edfi HLV Ancelotti v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2012. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi gi\u1edd, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n t\u1edbi 33 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i Ligue 1.</div>\r\n<h2>Xavi khuy\u00ean Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Rabiot</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Xavi kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i b\u00e0y t\u1ecf hy v\u1ecdng Barca c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Rabiot. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Clement Lenglet c\u0169ng \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng gia nh\u1eadp Camp Nou.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cRabiot l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt th\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eeba. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m cho Barca. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Nh\u01b0ng d\u1eabu sao, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u1eabn \u0111ang d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u1ee9c tin \u0111\u1ed3n\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 PSG:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/thuyen-truong-psg-nong-long-duoc-lam-viec-voi-mbappe-197-191791.html\">Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng PSG n\u00f3ng l\u00f2ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Mbappe</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-bayern-munich-31-psg-icc-2018-329-191756.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Bayern Munich 3-1 PSG (ICC 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4501","checkdouble":"191803"},{"date":"18:46 22/07","title":"B\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0103n v\u1ea1, Neymar kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m ch\u1ea5p s\u1ef1 \"thi\u1ebfu hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/bi-chi-trich-an-va-neymar-khong-them-chap-su-thieu-hieu-biet.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ng\u00f4i sao Brazil ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n k\u1ecbch k\u1ec7ch c\u1ee1m c\u1ee7a anh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eb1m m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n kh\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Brazil m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi ch\u1ec9 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00e0 thua B\u1ec9. Theo m\u1ed9t l\u1ebd t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u thi\u1ebfu c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng, Neymar v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean c\u0169ng ch\u1ecbu s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 nh\u1ea5t. Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 26 tu\u1ed5i thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf PSG v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n \u0103n v\u1ea1 k\u1ec7ch c\u1ee1m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean th\u00ec \u201ccon giun x\u00e9o l\u1eafm c\u0169ng qu\u1eb1n\u201d, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Neymar \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch khi thanh minh cho l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3ng k\u1ecbch v\u00e0 ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eb1m m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n kh\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0103n v\u1ea1, kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m ch\u1ea5p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Neymar \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0103n v\u1ea1, kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m ch\u1ea5p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/neymar-tran-tinh-ve-ly-do-an-va.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Neymar \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0103n v\u1ea1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cC\u00e1c ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mong b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u0103n ra s\u00e2n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady sao? Kh\u00f4ng, \u0111au l\u1eafm \u0111\u1ea5y. Sau m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u00f4i to\u00e0n ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 c\u00f3 khi \u0111\u1ebfn 4-5 ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01b0\u1eddm \u0111\u00e1.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cChuy\u1ec7n n\u00f3 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e2u, nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1edfi ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m n\u00f3.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u00f4i th\u00ec c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m ch\u1ea5p, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ec9 coi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng nh\u01b0 tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00f9a cho m\u00ecnh m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, t\u00f4i c\u00f2n ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u0103ng l\u00ean Instagram v\u1ec1 video l\u0169 tr\u1ebb b\u1eaft ch\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00ecnh c\u01a1 m\u00e0.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cB\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi k\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecbch v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng r\u00ea d\u1eaft v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e2u th\u1ec3 c\u1ee9 th\u1ebf n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng \u2018C\u01b0ng \u00e0, xin l\u1ed7i nh\u01b0ng l\u00e0m \u01a1n tr\u00e1nh ra \u0111\u1ec3 anh ghi b\u00e0n\u2019. \u0110\u00f3, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e2u th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m v\u1eady khi anh ta c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua, c\u00f2n anh ta c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i. Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i x\u1ea3y ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n r\u1ed3i sao khi t\u00f4i v\u1ed1n nhanh v\u00e0 nh\u1eb9 h\u01a1n \u0111a s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, th\u1ebf n\u00ean m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i l\u00e0 v\u00ec v\u1eady.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/kaka-bao-ve-brazil-va-neymar-sau-ky-world-cup-that-vong-421-191694.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/kaka-bao-ve-brazil-va-neymar-sau-ky-world-cup-that-vong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/kaka-bao-ve-brazil-va-neymar-sau-ky-world-cup-that-vong-421-191694.html\">Kaka b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Neymar sau k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</span><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Samba ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee9ng m\u0169i ch\u1ecbu s\u00e0o m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Brazil ch\u1ec9 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/alves-bao-ve-neymar-vi-thoi-an-va-197-191719.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/12/alves-bao-ve-neymar-vi-thoi-an-va.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/alves-bao-ve-neymar-vi-thoi-an-va-197-191719.html\">Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 l\u0169 kh\u00f4ng n\u00e3o m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Neymar</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng x\u1ea5u m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil t\u1ea1o ra t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t leo thang, v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Dani Alves l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Neymar tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4500","checkdouble":"191792"},{"date":"20:03 22/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 22/7: Chelsea nh\u1eafm chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao tr\u1ebb MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-227-chelsea-nham-chieu-mo-sao-tre-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 22/7.</h2><h2>Chelsea nh\u1eafm chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Martial\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 227 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 227 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/13/MU-muon-mua-Kylian-Mbappe-thay-Anthony-Martial-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 22/7:&nbsp;Chelsea nh\u1eafm chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Martial</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd The Times, Chelsea \u0111ang t\u00ednh to\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao tr\u1ebb Anthony Martial t\u1eeb Man United. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Eden Hazard mong mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Real Madrid, The Blues \u0111ang lao v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. V\u00e0 Martial \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u ti\u00ean. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Man United \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 Martial 100 tri\u1ec7u euro. Bayern c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Martial v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed r\u1ebb h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<h2>Man City d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Pjanic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Sport Mediaset kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Miralem Pjanic t\u1eeb Juventus h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Chelsea v\u00e0 Barcelona c\u0169ng \u0111ang b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Man xanh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi c\u1ea3 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1eadt c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Pjanic v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i hay ra \u0111i do Juve v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng si\u00eau sao Ronaldo.</div>\r\n<h2>MU ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n sao tr\u1ebb Rochdale</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Mirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man United \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n sao tr\u1ebb Daniel Adshead c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ea1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi Rochdale. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 17 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c theo d\u00f5i b\u1edfi h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Premier League. Anh \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp k\u00edn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i U23 MU v\u00e0 \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 1 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<h2>Klopp ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Pulisic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jurgen Klopp th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t th\u00edch sao tr\u1ebb Christian Pulisic. Nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c Liverpool s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng n\u00e0y. Theo chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c, l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pulisic.</div>\r\n<h2>Hart mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Man City</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Joe Hart \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Man City \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. G\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Hart \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn Torino r\u1ed3i sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 West Ham theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, Hart v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh.</div>\r\n<h2>Neymar x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u1edf l\u1ea1i PSG</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Neymar m\u1edbi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1m v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Real Madrid. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Real cho d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 12 th\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-2207-mu-nhan-cau-tra-loi-vu-sao-khung-croatia-184-191766.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 22/07: MU nh\u1eadn c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-217-choang-voi-muc-gia-kinh-hoang-cua-hang-thai-mu-184-191748.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 21/7: Cho\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 kinh ho\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i M.U</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4499","checkdouble":"191793"}]}